2578446abcd26512f","tid":1167661,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"就咁睇咗情報， 路飛因為坐監而變咗成件事嘅路人。<br />\n本來每一個島報仇個位都係由路飛去做。<br />\n依家變咗卓洛同山治去報仇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣睇嘅話， 路飛冇份打大蛇直接飛入去打凱多。 路飛/基德/羅三人組？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卓洛斬大蛇。 幫公主小南霜月家多康同財神鎮嘅人報仇。<br />\n 再加上佢師傅耕四郎喺和之國應該係一個有身份嘅人。 呢條線應該之後會講。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不死鳥對KING<br />\n鳥系，王副對決<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n山治秒咗一個台柱，打監獄Q就岩架啦（ 甚平可以幫拖） 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓狗報仇打J。<br />\n<br />\n其餘赤霄九人組同草帽團，應該各司其職， 對KO大蛇城堡入面嗰班忍者/台柱等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以剩餘果三個超新星， 打碟音， 占卜佬， 恐龍男。 應該會喺關鍵時刻企咗喺路飛嗰一邊一齊背叛凱多。"},{"pid":"19ec76902259970cb8d7118afbf2e74a4e693ae7","tid":1167661,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"赤霄九人組VS 1-9？？？？"},{"pid":"d57105cae6bc4ec4bec13ba051b65d719e0d0feb","tid":1167661,"uid":139538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"失去哭自由<br />\n<br />\n真係sad"},{"pid":"bfd546ea3948f8bdb7e3cbcdce56dda7e45b06e7","tid":1167661,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"大蛇既做法真係同共產黨一樣。<br />\n為左權利污染國家山河"},{"pid":"5ddd6a1da09e3062a513ef7928e865b9c1d4d286","tid":1167661,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrDV3j1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrDV3j1.jpg&h=bc18aa77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57e28550d4e65689977e52b60ffe43548aaafe54","tid":1167661,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ca7b0da76d447524d22db12e7a85e4eb9cdadd0b","tid":1167661,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5ddd6a1da09e3062a513ef7928e865b9c1d4d286","tid":1167661,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/